System preparation for biased simulations (States A and B)

The final configuration from step 4 of the system-preparation workflow was used. The simulation box was extended along the z-direction to expose the {001} face, resulting in box dimensions of 3.74711 × 3.95170 × 18.20000 nm³.
10 THE, 10 ASP, and 6286 water molecules were added. Final solvated structure: THE170ASP170H2O6286Face001.gro

1. Energy minimization
Performed using gromacs-energy-minimization.mdp, following the same protocol as the seed crystal.

2. NVT equilibration
Temperature equilibration performed using gromacs-nvt-equilibration-md-parameters-base.mdp.

3. NPT equilibration (semi-isotropic NPT)
Performed using gromacs-npt-md-parameters-base.mdp, modified for three consecutive stages:
i) 100 ps, 2 fs time step
ii) 100 ps, 0.5 fs time step
iii) 250 ps, 2 fs time step
Simulation continued after stage 3 for 20 ns.

4. NVT production
1000 ps NVT run using gromacs-nvt-md-parameters-base.mdp with a 2 fs time step.

5. Center-of-mass (COM) restraint
Applied after NVT production simulations using plumed.dat using gromacs-nvt-md-parameters-base.mdp file :
i) 1 ns with 1 k restraint
ii) 1 ns with 100 k restraint
iii) 1 ns with 1000 k restraint
iv) 25 ns with 1000 k restraint

6. Analysis – Surface Structure CV, and Edge-adsorption CVs, Biased CV
  i) Surface structure CV
    Calculated by post-processing the final restrained NVT trajectory (25 ns, 1000 k COM restraint).Files given for calculating surface structure CV for O1 atoms of THE-4A layer.; the same strategy can be applied to define surface structure CVs for other layers
Workflow:
            a) Run driver.sh in y_THE_O1 and z_THE_O1 folders.
            b) Run get_surface_structure_CV_parameter_values.py in corresponding folders to get CV parameters.
            c) For each folder THE_O1_y_row_1 to THE_O1_y_row_4: first run driver.sh in the corresponding x_THE_O1 subfolder, then run get_surface_structure_CV_parameter_values.py in the same folder to compute the CV parameters

  ii) Edge-adsorption CVs

